===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}}, from {{etyl|xno|en}} {{term|criminal|lang=fro}}, from {{etyl|LL.|en}} {{term|criminalis|lang=la}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|crimen||lang=la|crime}}

===Pronunciation===
